00:01:46.940 --> 00:01:47.940
Ted.

00:01:47.940 --> 00:01:50.940
Part of the gang here on Hey Dude.

00:01:50.940 --> 00:01:52.940
Oh, Ted McGrath.

00:01:52.940 --> 00:01:53.940
Never heard of him.

00:01:53.940 --> 00:01:55.940
Only on Nickelodeon.

00:01:56.940 --> 00:01:58.940
Now it's time for the Pizza Head Show.

