Hey everybody, our team's playing a big game right now,

00:02:00.940 --> 00:02:03.940
but I'm really excited because afterwards we're all going to Pizza Hut.

00:02:03.940 --> 00:02:04.940
Yay!

00:02:04.940 --> 00:02:05.940
Not so fast, Pizza Head.

00:02:05.940 --> 00:02:07.940
