00:50:04.850 --> 00:50:07.850
No one else seemed too concerned about it.

00:50:07.850 --> 00:50:09.850
But no matter how hard I tried,

00:50:09.850 --> 00:50:12.850
I couldn't stop wondering what was in there.

00:50:12.850 --> 00:50:14.850
It was like some black hole

00:50:14.850 --> 00:50:18.850
