00:52:27.160 --> 00:52:31.160
It was a policy I knew would deliver.

00:52:32.160 --> 00:52:35.160
Getting Slurm out of my way was the easy part.

00:52:35.160 --> 00:52:39.160
It was diverting endless Mike that made me a little squirmy.

